        "description": "<div><p>The Giant Spider lunges at a target, attempting to sink its serrated fangs into their flesh. It makes a melee attack, dealing D4 Piercing damage on a hit. If the attack hits, the target must succeed on an Endurance check or be Poisoned (1).</p></div>"
