    "description": "<div><p>This arachnid monstrosity weaves intricate webs that easily ensnare any creature unfortunate enough to walk into them. Its hairy, jet-black body is marked with crimson patterns, signaling the venomous threat it poses. Eight beady eyes, each glinting with predatory intelligence, survey its surroundings with an uncanny awareness, while its serrated fangs drip with a potent neurotoxin.</p></div>",
